# RohanRice Marketplace - Frontend

## Environment Variables

Create a `.env.local` file in the project root with the following variables:

```env
# API Configuration
NEXT_PUBLIC_API_BASE_URL=http://localhost:8000
NEXT_PUBLIC_SOCKET_URL=http://localhost:5000

# Next Auth
NEXTAUTH_URL=http://localhost:3000
NEXTAUTH_SECRET=your-secret-key-here

# Google OAuth
NEXT_PUBLIC_GOOGLE_CLIENT_ID=your-google-client-id
GOOGLE_CLIENT_SECRET=your-google-client-secret

# Algolia (for AI Help)
NEXT_PUBLIC_ALGOLIA_APP_ID=NJDXOUYYQZ
NEXT_PUBLIC_ALGOLIA_API_KEY=d27e261dd1ecda23f8728e60f9b23d21
NEXT_PUBLIC_ALGOLIA_INDEX_NAME=rohanrice_index

# reCAPTCHA
NEXT_PUBLIC_RECAPTCHA_SITE_KEY=your-recaptcha-site-key
RECAPTCHA_SECRET_KEY=your-recaptcha-secret-key

# Email Service
SMTP_HOST=smtp.gmail.com
SMTP_PORT=587
SMTP_USER=your-email@gmail.com
SMTP_PASS=your-app-password

# Database
DATABASE_URL=postgres://user:password@localhost:5432/rohanrice

# Node Environment
NODE_ENV=development
```

## Installation

```bash
npm install
```

## Development

```bash
npm run dev
```

Open [http://localhost:3000](http://localhost:3000) with your browser.

## Build

```bash
npm run build
npm start
```

## Features

- ✅ Premium rice marketplace
- ✅ Responsive design (mobile, tablet, desktop)
- ✅ Google OAuth & OTP authentication
- ✅ CAPTCHA verification
- ✅ Real-time AI help widget (Algolia)
- ✅ Admin dashboard
- ✅ Stock management
- ✅ Order tracking
- ✅ Ledger system
- ✅ Real-time messaging
- ✅ SEO optimized
- ✅ Vercel deployment ready

## API Endpoints

- `POST /api/auth/login` - Email/password login
- `POST /api/auth/request-otp` - Request OTP code
- `POST /api/auth/verify-otp` - Verify OTP & login
- `POST /api/contact` - Submit contact inquiry
- `POST /api/ai-help` - AI help queries

## Deployment

### Vercel

1. Connect your GitHub repository to Vercel
2. Add environment variables in Vercel dashboard
3. Vercel will auto-deploy on git push

```bash
vercel deploy --prod
```

### Manual Deployment

```bash
npm run build
npm start
```

## Browser Support

- Chrome 90+
- Firefox 88+
- Safari 14+
- Edge 90+
- Mobile browsers (iOS Safari 14+, Chrome Android)

